# Research Question Formulation

## Gap → Problem Statement
"Despite [what exists], [gap] remains because [root cause]. This causes [consequence]."

## RQ Template
"How can [method] be designed to [goal] in [context/constraint]?"

## Sub-questions: 2-4, each answerable in 1 paper/chapter

## Hypothesis
- H0: Method performs no better than baseline
- H1: Method achieves ≥X% improvement over baseline

## Contribution Types
Algorithm / Framework / Dataset / Benchmark / Analysis / System / Theorem

## Quality Check
Specific + Feasible + Novel + Significant + Ethical
